## 2. Side-effect-avoidance design principles (CMT-specific 7 axes)

각 hxq-cmt-* 후보가 거쳐야 할 design-time constraint set. Phase β SMILES commit 시 explicit audit gate.

| 축 | 회피 대상 (clinical lesson)                                                                                                | design-time constraint                                                                                                                                | 본 roadmap 적용 후보            |
|----|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| 1  | **CNS 부작용** — 자율신경 / 인지 / 진정 (PXT3003 baclofen-naltrexone 교훈, ricolinostat 전신 HDAC6)                          | 말초 한정 — P-gp substrate by polar mass + 양친매성 불균형 + GalNAc/SQ conjugate + Schwann-tropic capsid + muscle-specific promoter (tMCK-class)  | hd6-001, clc1-001, gjb1-001     |
| 2  | **HNPP overshoot** — PMP22 silencing 과도 시 결손 phenotype                                                                | 가역 + dosage-titratable (siRNA/ASO > CRISPR-DNA 편집) + dose-response audit gate + escape rescue 옵션 (capping siRNA antagonist)                     | pmp22-001, pmp22-002             |
| 3  | **Innate immune (TLR) — siRNA/ASO cytokine release**                                                                       | 2'-OMe + 2'-F + PS backbone + 5' capping + GU-rich motif 회피 + LNP 회피 (chronic dosing safety)                                                       | pmp22-001, pmp22-002             |
| 4  | **Reversibility — covalent / suicide-substrate chronic toxicity**                                                          | 가역 non-covalent binding 우선; covalent 필요 시 reversible-covalent (boronate / nitrile) + 짧은 t1/2 + reactivation kinetics audit                | hd6-001, sar1-001, mfn2-001      |
| 5  | **Paralog cross-reactivity** — HDAC1/2/3 (cytopenia), ClC-2/Kb (urolithiasis), ErbB1/4 (cardiotoxicity), Cx26 (deafness) | selectivity ratio ≥500-1000 audit; in-silico VQE selectivity scan 의무; mutant-selective fold-rescue / allele-specific design 우선                    | hd6-001, clc1-001, nrg1-001, gjb1-001 |
| 6  | **Liver/kidney chronic accumulation** — 만성 dosing safety                                                                | miR-122 BS 3'UTR (AAV) / GalNAc 외 conjugate / SQ-Schwann 한정 / urinary excretion route monitoring                                                  | pmp22-001/002, fig4-001          |
| 7  | **AAV vector immunogenicity** — pre-existing nAb seropositive (~30-50% 인구) + insertional + 2nd dose 불가                 | de-immunized capsid + empty-capsid decoy + AAVrh / synthetic capsid + tissue-detarget 3'UTR (miR-122 / miR-142 / miR-183) + 2nd-dose strategy 사전 계획 | fig4-001, (잠재 nrg1 AAV-arm)   |

(constraint vs candidate 매트릭스 = design-time gate. Phase β build 단계에서 후보별 audit checklist 자동화.)

